{"pageProps":{"source":"<div class=\"space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0\"><p>Il existe plusieurs façons de démarrer un serveur HTTP en ligne de commande.</p><h2>Python</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">python3 -m http.server 5000\n</code></pre></div><h2>PHP</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">php -S 0.0.0.0:5000\n</code></pre></div><h2>Nodejs (http-server)</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">npm i -g http-server\nhttp-server -p 5000\n</code></pre></div><h2>Nodejs (serve)</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">npm i -g serve\nserve\n</code></pre></div><h2>Miniserve</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo pacman -S miniserve\nminiserve\n</code></pre></div><h2>Webfsd</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">yay -S --noconfirm webfs\nwebfsd -F -p 5000\n</code></pre></div><hr/><p>Références :</p><ul>\n<li>https://gist.github.com/willurd/5720255</li>\n<li>https://github.com/rejetto/hfs/</li>\n<li>\n<a title=\"Note bientôt disponible\" class=\"!no-underline border-b-2 border-dotted border-cyan-700\" href=\"/soon?title=Nginx\">Nginx</a>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<a title=\"Note bientôt disponible\" class=\"!no-underline border-b-2 border-dotted border-cyan-700\" href=\"/soon?title=Apache\">Apache</a>\n\n</li>\n</ul></div>","isIndex":false,"file":"Serveur Web.md","fileName":"Serveur Web","title":"Démarrer un serveur HTTP en ligne de commande","comments":true,"permalink":"demarrer-un-serveur-http-en-ligne-de-commande","datePublished":"2021-07-05T16:31","dateUpdated":"2021-07-05T16:31","aliases":"[Server HTTP, Web server, Serveur HTTP, Serveur Web]","publish":true,"rss":true},"__N_SSG":true}